{
  "stem": "21788.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because he was used to this kind of clientele, the actors, the actresses, and all that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, he tried, and it was absolutely no way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He tried, actually, here in Denver to also open that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Didn't work.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He stayed here roughly about half a year, decided that it was not possible for him to make a living over here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Only other way to do is go back to Santiago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He went back to Santiago, was able to buy back most of his very specialized sewing machines, and was in business again for a very short time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The communists took over, took his business away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By that time, he was old enough to be eligible for social security.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Social security from-- not from Santiago, social security from Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he decided, I've had enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I'm going back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The incentive being that you can get a partial social security if you do not live in Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If you move back to Germany, you will get the full Social Security.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So that's what my uncle did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He did not go back to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Apparently, Berlin held too many bad memories for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He went to another very nice place, Baden-Baden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Baden-Baden is a resort for the rich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he lived within a stone's throw of the Baden-Baden casino.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I did visit him in 1971, and he had a very nice apartment with a balcony.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Did not really work anymore in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Matter of fact, he was quite sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He had a heart ailment, and that was the only time that I saw my uncle after he fled out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And a year later, he passed away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
